<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Hello from Demo Site</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: #020617;
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }
    main {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #22d3ee;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 36rem;
    }
    a {
      color: #38bdf8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <h1>Hello, world!</h1>
    <p>This is a simple test page served from the demo container behind Traefik. Use it to confirm routing behaviour and TLS termination.</p>
    <p><a href="/">Back to the main demo page</a></p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
